│ 737 /// An extension of the inner loop vectorizer that creates a skeleton for a            │
│ 738 /// vectorized loop that has its epilogue (residual) also vectorized.                  │
│ 739 /// The idea is to run the vplan on a given loop twice, firstly to setup the           │
│ 740 /// skeleton and vectorize the main loop, and secondly to complete the skeleton        │
│ 741 /// from the first step and vectorize the epilogue.  This is achieved by               │
│ 742 /// deriving two concrete strategy classes from this base class and invoking           │
│ 743 /// them in succession from the loop vectorizer planner.                               │
│ 744 class InnerLoopAndEpilogueVectorizer : public InnerLoopVectorizer {                    │
│ 745 public:                                                                                │
│ 746   InnerLoopAndEpilogueVectorizer(                                                      │
